               <p>Before Mr. Justice Gazelee.</p>
               <p>1750. 
               <persName id="t18280911-196-defend1145" type="defendantName">
                  JAMES 
                  COLLINS
               <interp inst="t18280911-196-defend1145" type="surname" value="COLLINS"></interp>
